Time":"2020-03-28T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"留喺香港把撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"人工高"},{"pid":"a8928c25a174a35f049c05ab5ba1c09d050183a3","tid":1947060,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"支持曾罷工醫護拎定一兩箱口罩過去搵食<br />\n<br />\nHA夠膽咪清算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0551883862cb769b437191de3b8a32d40ff00b","tid":1947060,"uid":241504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a81bad4e8c1a806c3e5091b0d14326a857ff65b7","tid":1947060,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bf30f5b3e6ddc480a0ebaeb1c8654c52992c973","tid":1947060,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d61f62d3ef237218957e7366221f543fa0b03ed","tid":1947060,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"樓主，幾時去？有綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"我無醫護資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計 薪酬都應該好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但未必有綠卡....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"有 mbbs 冇用<br />\n去美國做要考USMLE<br />\n<br />\n利申有mbbs"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#165028 - 天安門旅遊</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>誠哥真係好醒目 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>好怕d勇武派 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>（求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1994f5de6d917340b17581a1a2c9ca4ba68acb51","tid":1947060,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c